title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 4PM' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday afternoon’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Pick 4 4PM” game were:
8-4-3-3
(eight, four, three, three)
